Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.67,0:03:47.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  優  讓你陪我過來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.59,0:03:48.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小事一樁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.04,0:03:53.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過你至少要來參加一下晨練
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.87,0:04:11.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.92,0:04:15.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好  我叫黑衣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.58,0:04:16.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.76,0:04:20.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.57,0:04:31.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你來接我啊  謝謝真透
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.39,0:04:32.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝優
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.49,0:04:35.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛阿姨…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.91,0:04:37.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的  走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.16,0:04:51.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來你有戴上它的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.15,0:04:54.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手環
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.51,0:04:59.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我也替優做了一個
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.66,0:05:00.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也有？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.02,0:05:03.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟真透湊成一對
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.34,0:05:07.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝  謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.79,0:05:10.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.93,0:05:11.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.45,0:05:16.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃泉看起來挺開朗的  不過
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.27,0:05:18.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總感覺…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.31,0:05:23.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.87,0:05:26.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頭髮
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.07,0:05:33.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安靜一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.97,0:05:37.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}「拼貼畫」
