Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.27,0:05:58.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃泉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.29,0:06:01.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.44,0:06:04.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手  黃泉…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.92,0:06:06.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手  黃泉…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.95,0:06:09.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳥遊  你在幹什麼  快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.51,0:06:10.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃泉  黃泉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.47,0:06:11.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快把剪刀交上來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.16,0:06:15.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃泉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.01,0:06:28.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說她父母過來把她帶回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.88,0:06:30.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可怕  真的好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.24,0:06:32.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說了
