Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.84,0:06:36.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說了別說了別說了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.49,0:06:45.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃泉  壞掉了
