Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.96,0:07:02.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,動手了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.02,0:07:05.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然打小篝  好過分
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.76,0:07:06.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小篝  沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.93,0:07:16.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.67,0:07:18.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.46,0:07:20.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.20,0:07:22.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝咖啡嗎
