Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.64,0:07:28.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.00,0:07:31.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是提了下建議而已
